data.description: This beautiful home sits in a quiet cul-de-sac within a short walking distance of Lake Willastein Park. New wood laminate flooring and new interior paint throughout. The large master bathroom features his and hers closets, walk in shower, walk in tub, and large skylight providing great natural light. Just off the living room are beautiful french doors leading to the home office/library. In the back yard is a spacious patio  great for entertainment as well as a large shed for additional storage. Other great features include Nest smart climate control system and fiberoptic internet capabilities. Schedule your tour to see everything this wonderful home has to offer.
